@Node "FAQ" "4D-Clock.guide/FAQ"
@Toc "Main"

@{fg shine}FAQ@{fg text}

Frequently Asked Questions


@{b}Q:@{ub} I get error messages like "can't open agl.library".
    Where can i get this library?

@{b}A:@{ub} You don't have a propper StormMesa installation.
    All these librarys are part of StormMesa.
    If you don't already have StormMesa, download it from:

    http://www.haage-partner.com/3dworld/index-e.htm


@{b}Q:@{ub} Why don't you include StormMesa into your distribution?

@{b}A:@{ub} It's too big.


@{b}Q:@{ub} My Computer crashes when starting 4D-Clock.

@{b}A:@{ub} Set the stack space to 300000. This helps in most cases.


@{b}Q:@{ub} Do i need a 3D-accelerator?

@{b}A:@{ub} No. If you don't have a 3D-accelerator, the 3D-output is rendered
    by the cpu. If you have a 3D-accelerator, you will also need
    Warp3D to use it.


@endnode
